[src:shadow-dom/attachshadow] This example demonstrates manual slot assignment.
[src:shadow-dom/attachshadow] With this approach, each element must be manually assigned to a particular slot using `HTMLSlotElement.assign()`.
[src:shadow-dom/attachshadow] There is no default assignment, so any slot that is not assigned will be empty.
